viewed at the <a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/feeds.htm\">Edu_RSS Feeds Page</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'Friday', '<h2>Research</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Research Topics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This page lists the research topics covered in this website.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/research_topics.htm\">Topics</a></li>\r\n<li><a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/research_authors.htm\">Authors</a></li>\r\n<li><a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/research_journals.htm\">Publications</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Research Wiki</strong></p>\r\n<p>The research wiki has returned.<br/><a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/wiki.cgi\">Research Wiki</a><br/>\r\nYou may edit the research wiki if you are logged in, not otherwise, sorry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Edu_RSS</strong></p>\r\n<p>Edu_RSS 0.2 is an application that allows you to define your own community of RSS feeds, aggregates content from those feeds and organizes it, and helps you integrate that content into your own posts, articles and other content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss02.htm\">About Edu_RSS</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On this site, Edu_RSS runs several different lists:<ul>\r\n<li><a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/edubloggers.htm\">Edu_RSS Edubloggers</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/news---ed.htm\">Edu_RSS News---Ed</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/media.htm\">Edu_RSS Media</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/design.htm\">Edu_RSS Design</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/cyberculture.htm\">Edu_RSS Cyberculture</a></li>\r\n<li><a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/ideas.htm\">Edu_RSS Ideas</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Feeds harvested by Edu_RSS may be viewed at the <a style=\"color: #0fad0f; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss/feeds.htm\">Edu_RSS Feeds Page</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'none', NULL, 'new__header.txt', 'new__footer.txt', 'no', 'no', 'no', '1', 1125691831, 1364861465, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, NULL, NULL, 'research.htm', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2'),
(35, 'Hiatus FAQ', NULL, NULL, 'htm', 'FAQ', NULL, 'Friday', '<h1>Hiatus FAQ</h1>\n\n<p><i>Huh? What? Are you ill or dying or something?</i></p>\n\n<p>No, my health is fine, get those thoughts out of your head.</p>\n\n<p><i>So, what then?</i></p>\n\n<p>There isn\'t a simple answer to that. Yes, there was an event that triggered it, internal to our organization, which I don\'t really think I should discuss. But this has been building up for a while, and is a combination of factors.</p>\n\n<p>I won\'t give you a glib answer like \'I needed a break\' nor will I simply say \'I need a rest\'. But these are factors, and they make it harder to handle the various stresses in my life. There\'s nothing deep you need to understand here, nothing I\'ll talk about anyways.</p>\n\n<p><i>You haven\'t been fired, have you?</i></p>\n\n<p>No. And my somewhat sudden disappearance may disconcert my employers but I don\'t believe they\'ll over-react. If they do, you\'ll be the first to know.</p>\n\n<p><i>But, are you ok?</i></p>\n\n<p>Not particularly (I mean, d\'uh) but I will be fine. Please don\'t worry about me. Think of this as a preventative measure rather than an emergency.</p>\n\n<p><i>Can I help? Is there anything I can do?</i></p>\n\n<p>Not really. I know who I can ask if I need anything (and thank you for your offers). I will be by myself for a while, but I know that I am not alone.</p>\n\n<p><i>Ah, you\'ll be alone. Where?</i></p>\n\n<p>I\'ll tell you later.</p>\n\n<p><i>When will you be back?</i></p>\n\n<p>I don\'t want to say for sure yet. I have a time in mind, but I also realize that things don\'t always work according to a schedule and I will not hesitate to change things.</p>\n\n<p><i>You are scheduled to be at our event. Will you be there?</i></p>\n\n<p>Yes. If anything changes, I will let you know right away. But I have no plans to cancel any events.</p>\n\n<p>That does not mean my hiatus will end at that point, it just means I will appear as scheduled.</p>\n\n<p><i>Can I still at least email you? Phone you?</i></p>\n\n<p>Not for a while. I\'m sorry I can\'t respond right now, but it\'s not really a hiatus if I have to do stuff.</p>\n\n<p><i>So it\'s just a vacation then.</i></p>\n\n<p>Well, no. It\'s a time for me to think and re-examine things. I\'m not simply taking a break. I have taken breaks before, you haven\'t noticed because I still write (usually more, in fact) and produce OLDaily. I actually <i>like</i> doing these things; it\'s not a hardship for me.</p>\n\n<p><i>So OLDaily will be back just like normal then.</i></p>\n\n<p>That\'s one of the things I have to think about.</p>\n\n<p><i>But what will I do for news?</i></p>\n\n<p>Edu_RSS is still running and, barring any disaster. You can <a href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?page=23\">view the recent listings here</a>. You can learn <a href=\"http://www.downes.ca/edurss02.htm\">about Edu_RSS here</a>.</p>\n\n<p><i>Phew! So you\'re coming back soon then, right?</i></p>\n\n<p>Soon enough, but not until I\'m clear about what I want to do and how I want to do it.</p>\n\n\n', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'no', 'no', 'no', '1', 1141778123, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, NULL, NULL, 'hiatusfaq.htm', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2'),
(16, 'Most Popular Links', NULL, NULL, 'htm', '<p>The most popular links on Stephen&#39;s Web, as measured by readership.</p>', '<h2>Hits This Year</h2>\r\n<p></p><ol>\r\n<keyword db=post;id GT 61604;all;format=link_hits;total GT 100;sort=crdate;type=link;number=10000;all>\r\n</ol>', 'Friday', '<h1>Best of OLDaily</h1>\r\n<div class=\"post_description\">This page lists the most popular links cited on OLDaily, based on the number of times readers view them. Not perfect; expect bugs. News is updated every weekday. For more information and to subscribe to OLDaily by email or RSS, <a href=\"http://www.downes.ca/news/\">click here</a>. </div>\r\n<keyword db=link;number=20;expires=172;sort=hits DESC>', 'none', 'HTML', NULL, NULL, 'no', 'no', 'no', '1', 1125691866, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, NULL, NULL, 'popular.htm', NULL, 'no', '00', '00', NULL, NULL, 'no', 'Never', '0', '2');
