n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3870</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/\">none</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>Web Analytics, Anyone?</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3869</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[As Abbott &#38; Costello demonstrate in this classic video, if you don&#8217;t ask the right question, you can end up going around in circles without ever answering the pertinent questions. As anyone who has worked with web analytics knows, there is a dizzying amount of information available to measure user behavior on your web site. [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 22, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 22 Nov 2012 08:05:44 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3869</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/201\">Video</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>What Social Online Experience Do Students Expect from Your School?</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3867</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[Technology has enabled students and colleges to accomplish a lot online. Gone are the days of waiting in line to register for classes or even sitting in a classroom! More colleges are moving courses, orientations and administrative tasks online. Sounds great and efficient, right? Yes, but if you\'ve read our new eBook, you know that [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:37 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3867</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/119\">Schools</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>It Doesn\'t Matter What YOU Think</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3868</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[I once got in an extremely heated debate with several people who were passionately opposed to one idea: Flash mobs. They argued their point for a good half hour, raising their voices, climbing up on chairs, accusing me of catering to the lowest common denominator. You would have thought I kicked a puppy. What they [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:37 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3868</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/\">none</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>Why MOOCS Should Be In Your Marketing Plan</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3865</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[As reported on the Daily Texan, student debt hit $914 billion during this year&#8217;s second quarter. Unemployment stood at 8.3 percent during the summer season. With increasing student debt numbers and the struggling job market, a college education seems to be an exponential monetary burden that weighs little in the competitive, idle job market. As [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:36 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3865</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/172\">Online Learning</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>Build your social strategy in Social Media Marketing Boot Camp. Get $50 off with code GURU50</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3866</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[Sometimes we come across offers that we think would be really interesting/valuable to the community that we want to pass along. The following is a guest post from Mediabistro promoting their Social Media Marketing Boot Camp where .eduGuru readers can also get a $50 discount if you choose to sign up. How are you building [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:36 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3866</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/\">none</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>84% of Schools Report Traditional Marketing Methods Alone Are Not Enough</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3863</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[To anyone who has been reading this blog for any amount of time the headline here isn\'t anything new. We might have felt this way for years, but a new report by CUnet finally gives us the data we have been looking for to support our gut feeling. This report has some very revealing numbers, [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:35 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3863</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/119\">Schools</category>\n      <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/153\">Web Logs</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>OPENBLOCKPresentationCLOSEBLOCK Understanding Your Marketing Funnel</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3864</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[Last week I spoke on a panel at the University Aviation Association annual conference. As part of this panel each presenter was asked to put together a short presentation on a subject. I focused mine on Understanding Marketing Funnels. Our regular readers have seen me write on this subject a lot because one of the [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:35 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3864</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/\">none</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>OPENBLOCKPresentationCLOSEBLOCK Inbound School Marketing: Is Your Website Helping the Bottom Line?</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3862</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[I had a couple of people ask about the slides from my presentation at HighEdWeb &#8217;12 yesterday so I&#8217;m happy to get these up here. The guys at Converge Consulting were awesome enough to livestream the presentation and you can view it here. (Sorry the first few minutes were cut off) Presentation Description: The rules [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:34 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>http://www.downes.ca/link/3862</guid>\r\n                <category domain=\"http://www.downes.ca/topic/119\">Schools</category>\n\r\n</item>\r\n<item>\r\n\r\n   <title>Retain Students with Social Media and... Viral Emails?</title>\r\n   <link>http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/edurss02.cgi?rd=3859</link>\r\n   <description><![CDATA[Are you looking for ways to start recruiting students for your school through social media? Attracting applicants to your college through emails and social media is bound to become an important part of your strategy if you expect to grow your enrollment in the coming years. Students are taking a more active part in the [...] <a  href=\"http://www.downes.ca/cgi-bin/page.cgi?feed=13\" class=\"stealth\">.eduGuru</a>, November 8, 2012.  \r\n   ]]></description>\r\n         <pubDate>Thu, 8 Nov 2012 09:05:33 -0400</pubDate>\r\n         <guid>